item.title: Reimagining the Possible – The Art of Change with Dr. Tasha Golden
item.description:
“I often say that creativity is rooted in refusal. That you refuse to accept that the world as it is, is just fine as it is, because  you recognize that the world as it is can be altered”. 


Dr. Tasha Golden wants everyone to see the extraordinary power in creativity. Tasha is a behavioral scientist, and a leading expert in how creativity drives transformative change. And she should know... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/67a23ec29a67c6bc4ec757ac
